    "body": "From my experience, the convenience of the separation are:\r\n1. We can make sure the lightweight `make lint` checks pass first, then try to make the heavyweight `make test` pass when developing.\r\n2. In CI result, it's clear to know the issue happens due to the correctness or just formatting.\r\n\r\nAn alternative solution to address it is adding a new `make test_and_lint` command. ",
